Detailed Description

cvmx_mdab::_rd_addr

The starting address used by the RD-DMA engine when writing RD-DMA data to local DSP memory. During Job_Type = LD_LCL commands, hardware loads the RD_ADDR/RD_LIMIT registers directly.
